- My friend Ga Eul's family.

385
00:41:25,590 --> 00:41:28,662
Also Ji Hoo Sunbae's Foundation.

386
00:41:28,662 --> 00:41:31,031
Just leave them alone.

387
00:41:31,031 --> 00:41:32,967
What's your offer?

388
00:41:32,967 --> 00:41:35,796
